you have &lt;span class=&quot;hljs-keyword&quot;&gt;to&lt;/span&gt; intialize &lt;span class=&quot;hljs-keyword&quot;&gt;while&lt;/span&gt; declaring itself &lt;span class=&quot;hljs-keyword&quot;&gt;as&lt;/span&gt; no way &lt;span class=&quot;hljs-keyword&quot;&gt;to&lt;/span&gt; assign
